Amazon Alexa and WeBack work together to help you control your devices easily.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
No need to manually control your device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
Connect Alexa and your WeBack smart devices by following steps:
(1). Download "WeBack" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Registered and login WeBack account in "WeBack" app;
(3). You need to have some WeBack smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in "WeBack" app and set the nickname of your devices(Easy to identify. The default is: robot, light, socket, etc.);
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "WeBack" skill from the "Alexa" app skills categories;
(8). Click "Enable" button of "WeBack" skill, and you'll be navigated to WeBack login page;
(9). Input your WeBack account and password, “log in”,you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, discover my devices"
"Alexa,turn on the robot."
"Alexa,turn off the robot."

